long_description: welcome to ignition mobile car valeting / detailing service. starting out with love of cars from a very young age the passion grew and grew to the point i see cars as a lot more than just a car. therefore they need the best quality care they can have. i use the very best ph neutral premium shampoos and luxury products on the market using yum, bear car care, autofinesse and garage therapy. i maintain a very strong work ethic and always use the safe wash 2 bucket method to keep the car free of any micro swirls or scratches. every car goes through a pre-wash stage. we use the best gtechniq wash mitts, fresh and new microfibre cloths and luxury yum drying towels. i also offer ceramic coatings, paint correction, polishing & waxing, sealants.
